item.title: CVE-2023-0067|2024-08-02T04:54:32.597Z -- unknown -- timed%20content
item.description: The Timed Content WordPress plugin before 2.73 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
